body:
@mrry Should we be escaping strings in error messages?  I vaguely recall having part of that discussion before.

@CRSilkworth The unicode error is secondary.  Your immediate problem is the `Could not parse example input` error.  @martinwicke Is this the dreaded protobuf limit?  The error is from https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/dfc5cd48a095b133ece9caff663e3cc512e8a268/tensorflow/core/kernels/example_parsing_ops.cc#L326.
